p.e:
ART COLLEGE PUT
ME THROUGH A HAZE.

IS IT STILL WORTH IT?
WAS ALL THAT MONEY
WORTH IT?

I'LL LET YOU KNOW WHEN
I FIND OUT.

I CRIED UNDER A DESK, SMASHED OREOS INTO
MY HEAD, AND FACED THOUGHTS THAT I THOUGHT
I HAD GROWN PAST.

I DOUBTED MYSELF AND MY ART. IT'S SOMETHING
EVERYONE FACES, BUT I DIDN'T KNOW IT AT THE TIME.
IT WASN'T NAIVEITY, I JUST DIDN'T THINK ABOUT IT.
